author: The Current
description:
Minneapolis music icon Mark Mallman‘s “Seen My Own Ghost” is a key track off his new paranormal concept album “Magic Time”. The writer, rocker, and historian will celebrate his 11th studio album’s release on August 8 @theparkwaympls. “Seen My Own Ghost” can be heard station-wide on The Current. Hit Play!

#markmallman #magictime #thecurrent #minnesotamusic #mpr #minnesota #thelocalshow
title: Mark Mallman talks about his track "Seen My Own Ghost" #MarkMallman #MagicTime
